    "class": "",
    "desc": "The final evolution of the F11 chassis. A turreted tank with the new YK-110 cannon was originally planned, but the chassis proved too old and unable to accomodate the heavier turret without significant cost overruns. The turreted project was instead restarted from the F16 chassis. The modernization work on the F11 chassis was instead reworked into a tank destroyer.",
